      • testEmptyVariableWidthVector

        public void testEmptyVariableWidthVector()
        Test to verify that record batch sizer handles the actual empty vectors correctly. RowSetBuilder by default allocates Drillbuf of 10bytes for each vector type which makes their capacity >0 and not ==0 which will be in case of empty vectors.
